## **Personal Digital Business Card Generator**

Create a tool that generates QR codes containing your contact information (vCard format). When someone scans it, they can instantly save your details to their phone.

**Features you could include:**
- Generate a QR code with your name, phone, email, and social media links
- Customize QR code colors and add a logo in the center
- Save different versions (high-res for printing, web-optimized)
- Create a simple GUI where you can input different contact details
- Generate multiple cards for different contexts (professional, personal, etc.)

**Bonus ideas:**
- Make QR codes for WiFi credentials that auto-connect when scanned
- Create a URL shortener with custom QR codes
- Build a QR code menu generator for restaurants
- Make an event check-in system with unique QR codes
